text: Ahmad Abbas Hattab Al-Saedi (Arabic: احمد عباس حطاب الساعدي, born May 9, 1994) is an Iraqi footballer who plays as a center midfielder for Al-Talaba in Iraq. Hattab made his International debut against Yemen in the 21st Arabian Gulf Cups on 12 January 2013. ==References== == Other websites == * profile on goalzz.com Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Living people Category:1993 births
